terrapeer.vui.j3dui.control.actuators
Class TransformGroupPlugin

java.lang.Object
  terrapeer.vui.j3dui.control.actuators.ActuatorPlugin
      terrapeer.vui.j3dui.control.actuators.TransformGroupPlugin
Direct Known Subclasses:
MMTransformGroupPlugin, SMTransformGroupPlugin, SVTransformGroupPlugin
public abstract class TransformGroupPlugin
extends ActuatorPlugin

Abstract base class for an actuator plugin that manipulates a TransformGroup target node. The manner in which the transform geometry is manipulated is specified by a geometry plugin, which also defines the format of the input actuation value.
